<div>
  <div style="max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    Hey <%= @user.fullname %>,

    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px;">
      Hope you are doing well.
      Maybe you heard already that VersionEye will shut down. 
      If you haven't heard yet then please read this <a href="https://blog.versioneye.com/2017/10/19/versioneye-sunset-process/">blog post</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
