      But there are still some contracts in place and some customers need a bit more time to
      migrate. That's why the service will stay alive for a couple more weeks. 
      Most likely til End of January.
    </p>
    <p>
      As we are shutting down operations soon, many users asked me 
      for alternative products. Here are some products which are similar to 
      VersionEye:
    </p>
    <p>
      <ul style="list-style-type: none">
